ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to add a provision that requires immigration documents to be automatically cancelled whenever a removal order is issued against an inadmissible foreign national.
